<td>ShowClix Ticketing LLC</td>
<td>Delivers tickets via SMS text message</td>
<td>Off-the shelf image scanner</td>
<td>Remote server</td>
<td>Rental of or investment for scanner devices</td>
<td>-</td>
<td>United States</td>
</tr>
