<td>Need to know phone model to send appropriate code.</td>
<td>Netherlands, Europe</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Trinity Mobile Limited</td>
<td>Barcode (SMS, MMS, WAP, NOKIA, EMS). Keyword Text-In/Push/WAP Purchase/Secure Interfaces</td>
<td>Barcode reader, PDA or Kiosk</td>
<td>Online lookup, local server or trickle fed PDA database. Wifi and GPRS</td>
